====Noun====
'''pants''' (''plural'')

# {{pluralia tantum}} A [[garment]] worn by men and women that covers the body from the [[waist]] downwards, usually as far as the [[ankle]]s; [[trousers]].
# {{context|UK|colloquial, not all areas|pluralia tantum}} A [[garment]] worn by men or women that covers the [[genitals]] and often the [[buttocks]] and the neighbouring parts of the body; [[panties]], [[shorts]].
# {{context|fashion industry}} {{rfv-sense}} {{plural of|[[pant]]}}

